Class JarScriptArchive.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.nicobar.core.archive.JarScriptArchive.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    JarScriptArchive

    public static class JarScriptArchive.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to Construct a JarScriptArchive. By default, this will generate a moduleId using the name of the jarfile, minus the ".jar" suffix.
